Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.02,0:00:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.70,0:00:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高莲小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.02,0:01:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮我把销售数据完整化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.02,0:01:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前会议的数据都没出来\N是 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.38,0:01:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天你这个资料也算错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.74,0:01:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我重算\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.50,0:01:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.86,0:01:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的\N商品开发也要好好做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.30,0:01:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也关系到我的将来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.02,0:02:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉 资料我会再审核的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.90,0:02:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资料不只要经过我\N还要经过社长啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.90,0:02:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N请大家好好加油好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不要再出错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.18,0:02:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情我不会再原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.78,0:02:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那嘴脸是怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.06,0:03:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也有男同事被她大骂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.58,0:03:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想被她当笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.82,0:03:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来想想怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.46,0:04:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门锁上 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.06,0:04:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.78,0:05:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 这样不好吧\N不会啦 大家都回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.38,0:05:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被看到啦\N会啦 会被听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.62,0:05:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不要吗\N那这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样\N好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.30,0:06:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服\N好好爽一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经很兴奋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.62,0:06:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服\N很舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.30,0:06:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 会被听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服吧\N很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.22,0:07:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头站起来啰\N硬起来了 哎呀 讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.82,0:08:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服喔\N舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.30,0:08:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会疯掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.78,0:08:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在吃零食喔\N因为很甜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.06,0:09:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服啊\N乳头都挺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.22,0:09:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长的技巧好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.82,0:09:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爱这样吧\N恩 好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 胸部给我舔舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.46,0:10:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.42,0:10:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内裤好可爱可以看到阴毛\N都被你看光光啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.42,0:11:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手指爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.54,0:11:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微屁股抬高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.22,0:11:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服\N你真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.70,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服 屁股摇一摇\N好淫荡的屁屁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.54,0:12:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰杆也很淫荡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.38,0:12:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那请你让我更淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.62,0:12:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:12:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.34,0:13:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看光光了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.14,0:13:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.26,0:14:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 不要看那么仔细
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.58,0:14:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啊 可以在这种地方做这种事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.30,0:14:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.66,0:14:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服\N好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.10,0:15:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会高潮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.74,0:15:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴巴油油的\N都是我的蜜汁喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.74,0:16:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道自己哪里湿湿吗\N当然是小穴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.66,0:16:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的小穴好好吃喔\N真的吗 好高兴喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.66,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再大胆一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.46,0:16:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方 好淫荡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.30,0:16:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴好烫喔\N对啊 变烫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.98,0:17:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很淫荡才这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.18,0:17:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.90,0:17:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超舒服的\N很爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.66,0:17:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高潮了 好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.14,0:17:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次把屁股抬高\N屁股吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要吃我屁屁吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.82,0:18:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.74,0:18:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已经备战状态了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.94,0:19:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让我看看你的吧\N哇 好厉害 要放进来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.02,0:19:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在忍耐着吗\N好像也湿透了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有精神喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗\N好吃极了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.58,0:19:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒\N硬梆梆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.50,0:20:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗\N超爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.86,0:20:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.54,0:20:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调一下姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.34,0:21:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变这么硬 好棒喔\N因为我很想干你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.46,0:21:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是很想做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.94,0:21:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有今天喔\N别说了快舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.74,0:21:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.10,0:21:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.14,0:22:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让女生等那么久\N当然这可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.22,0:22:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么想要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.58,0:22:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.06,0:22:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.50,0:22:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了 这样就爽\N我让你更爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.06,0:23:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦 部长\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.66,0:23:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了 去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.42,0:23:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 部长棒棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.22,0:23:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那边躺着\N让你知道什么叫棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.14,0:23:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗\N很好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.22,0:24:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进来我的小穴 听不到喔\N进来我的小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.62,0:24:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长硬硬的肉棒快进来\N我会让你爽个够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.62,0:24:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算被别人看到也没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.46,0:24:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用硬硬的肉棒插我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.22,0:24:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来了好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.74,0:24:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再进来一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.18,0:24:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.34,0:24:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小穴温暖吗\N很舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.94,0:25:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服喔\N舒服极了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.86,0:25:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.34,0:25:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的小穴最棒了\N很强吗 超舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.10,0:25:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.46,0:25:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.18,0:26:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.06,0:26:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.82,0:26:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开我看看嘛\N好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:46.42,0:26:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快进来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:02.26,0:27:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 要去了\N不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.86,0:27:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴道要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.90,0:27:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.18,0:27:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:46.90,0:27:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:49.94,0:27:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超棒的\N太好了 好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.30,0:28:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:20.98,0:28:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 我还要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.38,0:28:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样怎么样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.42,0:28:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:51.06,0:28:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看的到插好深喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.06,0:29:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:08.66,0:29:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面看的到吗\N看的到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:45.30,0:29:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒喔\N插得好深好深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.74,0:29:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长插得好深啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.34,0:30:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:10.90,0:30:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进来 你还满厉害的嘛\N那自己扳开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.10,0:30:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服 进来了 好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:28.98,0:30:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得好清楚喔\N那就仔细看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.34,0:30:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗\N舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:56.50,0:31:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢部长的肉棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.42,0:31:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.30,0:31:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服\N我快坏掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.30,0:31:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:24.50,0:32:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:44.34,0:32:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:59.54,0:33:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太大胆了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.34,0:33:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.90,0:33:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要射了\N我要部长的精液
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:27.86,0:33:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想要部长的精液
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:54.10,0:33:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服喔 部长\N你好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:05.78,0:34:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.97,0:34:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:25.45,0:34:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:05.46,0:35:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 射了好多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.74,0:35:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽不爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.94,0:35:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了\N同样的错要犯几次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:39.86,0:35:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么就不能多注意一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:48.18,0:35:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.54,0:35:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是接下来会议的数据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.14,0:36:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一小时嘛\N来做些什么吧 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:11.86,0:36:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家等了好久呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:19.38,0:36:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:27.70,0:36:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 XX公司的远藤部长找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:33.94,0:36:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远藤部长啊 可是要开会了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.66,0:36:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先看他要干嘛 我先准备一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.14,0:36:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了\N你好 我是部长秘书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.30,0:37:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长不方便接电活 有什么我可以帮忙的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.82,0:37:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N部长 别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:17.62,0:37:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:28.50,0:37:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.18,0:37:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北海道 85
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:44.50,0:37:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青森县 37
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.58,0:37:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩手县 42
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:03.06,0:38:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫城县 99
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.30,0:38:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:12.82,0:38:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 秋田县39
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:19.54,0:38:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.02,0:38:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山形县 54
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.50,0:38:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:38.10,0:38:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福岛 98
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:47.06,0:38:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茨城县 77
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.14,0:38:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栃木县 58
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:57.94,0:39:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长你\N你好好继续吧 要忍住喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:05.46,0:39:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思\N接下来是群马县 86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:15.86,0:39:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琦玉县 25
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.14,0:39:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是 你在干嘛啦\N部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:26.58,0:39:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被听到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:29.78,0:39:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千叶县 134
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:36.50,0:39:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京都 1795
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.02,0:39:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神奈川县 335
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:57.14,0:40:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新泻县 88
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:07.22,0:40:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长\N继续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:12.98,0:40:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:18.10,0:40:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来装上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:22.58,0:40:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 石川县 83
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:32.34,0:40:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福井县 58
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:46.90,0:40:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:50.26,0:40:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山形县 24
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:00.98,0:41:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长野县 73
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:12.82,0:41:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岐阜县 102
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:22.10,0:41:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静冈县 89
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:33.30,0:41:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你停下来部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:44.18,0:41:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是三重县 56
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:52.50,0:41:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滋贺县 45
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:57.94,0:42:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 京都是147
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:08.50,0:42:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大阪府 828
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.94,0:42:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兵库县 254
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:29.30,0:42:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈良县 59
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:35.06,0:42:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 你一直这样\N你继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:41.30,0:42:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会议来不及我不管你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:45.78,0:42:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 久等了 奈良县 59
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.78,0:43:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和歌山线 52
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:12.66,0:43:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟取县 30
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:26.58,0:43:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛根县 44
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:33.14,0:43:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冈山县 89
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.18,0:43:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广岛县 186
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:02.90,0:44:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山口县 75
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.74,0:44:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 你这样我很困扰 请别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:25.46,0:44:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:35.86,0:44:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山口县 75
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:46.10,0:44:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德岛 28
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:56.02,0:45:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忍耐了 快高潮吧\N不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:02.90,0:45:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去吧\N香川县 95
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:11.70,0:45:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:23.86,0:45:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:37.14,0:45:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦 会高潮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:48.98,0:45:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:52.82,0:45:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 真的会被听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:58.58,0:46:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:13.46,0:46:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 对不起\N失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:20.18,0:46:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高知县 55
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:24.66,0:46:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 不行啦\N为什么偏偏是现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:34.42,0:46:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.58,0:46:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:43.38,0:46:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:58.58,0:47:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:45.14,0:47:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请再稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:56.34,0:47:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:03.54,0:48:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:30.74,0:48:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了 要射啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:35.06,0:48:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:42.26,0:48:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:02.42,0:49:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:16.82,0:49:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:23.06,0:49:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再把资料给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:36.02,0:49:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:46.90,0:49:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近常加班\N是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:52.02,0:49:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近他们逼得比较紧\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:59.06,0:50:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近稍稍出错的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:04.82,0:50:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们讲话都超刻薄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:11.54,0:50:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人过这种严肃的生活会有男人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:21.14,0:50:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是长得不错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:30.58,0:50:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其我们偶尔也会想象一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:36.18,0:50:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长跟她如果有一腿可以拿来威胁她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:46.42,0:50:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是没有耶\N她怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:54.10,0:50:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有机会我也想上她\N我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:00.50,0:51:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这被知道应该会被杀\N她那么恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:07.54,0:51:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等一下要跟谁见面\NXX公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:29.62,0:51:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我再怎么说都会出错\N我马上改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:37.62,0:51:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出错只会浪费时间而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:44.82,0:51:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N社会人士要对自己负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:53.14,0:52:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是让你工作的地方 你不好好工作的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:02.74,0:52:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后尾小姐 过来一下\N部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:24.50,0:52:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的关系被发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:31.70,0:52:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N我刚刚在厕所听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:37.30,0:52:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道了\N怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:45.46,0:52:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被大家都知道的话\N我们会被炒鱿鱼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:52.66,0:52:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我考虑了很多\N我们已经交往半年了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:00.98,0:53:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该分了\N怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:09.62,0:53:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要离开部长\N我也不想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:16.34,0:53:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是曝光的话我们就死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:28.82,0:53:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好做的 别说什么分手的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:37.62,0:53:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 不想分手啊\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:44.50,0:53:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我说的话你都会做啰\N悉听尊便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:51.86,0:53:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会好好听话 对吧\N恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:59.54,0:54:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可以吗\N我知道了 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:07.70,0:54:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你等一下不要叫喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:18.26,0:54:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里吗 恩\N你那个时候不都叫很大声嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:24.82,0:54:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让我看看你能不能忍耐 在这种时期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:31.06,0:54:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来做吧\N大家会看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:38.10,0:54:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说是训练啊\N脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:44.34,0:54:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要脱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:48.34,0:54:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把奶罩脱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:53.62,0:54:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么不听话了\N可是这里会被看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:00.82,0:55:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就分手吧\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:05.78,0:55:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这不行\N不想分对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:10.74,0:55:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:37.94,0:55:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:43.22,0:55:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:48.02,0:55:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内裤脱掉 在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:51.86,0:55:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:05.14,0:56:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到\N那我们今天分手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:11.22,0:56:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:15.38,0:56:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被到的\N快点照办吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:19.22,0:56:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢我对吧\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:24.50,0:56:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好听我的话 知不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:53.46,0:56:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自慰吧\N好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:04.98,0:57:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被听到的话他们会困扰的\N把丝袜紧紧拉高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:13.62,0:57:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:21.94,0:57:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:28.66,0:57:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把胸罩脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:32.98,0:57:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:36.02,0:57:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在工作中喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:39.22,0:57:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有屏障没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:42.42,0:57:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你摆这种脸我会很不爽喔\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:00.98,0:58:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来这边脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:09.62,0:58:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:21.14,0:58:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长这样可以吗\N不行奶罩也脱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:26.26,0:58:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点照做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:50.10,0:58:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快脱的话 有人来怎么办\N部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:10.10,0:59:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:33.46,0:59:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:37.62,0:59:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:43.54,0:59:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:57.14,1:00:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长也要变硬喔\N我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:19.70,1:01:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:34.10,1:01:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:46.58,1:01:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:08.34,1:02:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会忍不住的\N在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:13.94,1:02:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:21.14,1:02:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:42.58,1:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 那里不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:01.14,1:03:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦 会被听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:06.26,1:03:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:14.42,1:03:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么就不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:17.62,1:03:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:21.30,1:03:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我先高潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:24.66,1:03:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真自私啊 对不起\N转过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:45.62,1:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:48.50,1:03:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的被发现啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:25.14,1:04:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要发出声音 对不起\N先把衣服穿起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:33.94,1:04:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用哪一件 白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:39.38,1:04:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以穿吗 快穿起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:49.62,1:04:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真淫荡 过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:21.62,1:05:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用普通的表情看大家\N看到了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:31.70,1:05:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:47.38,1:05:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:55.86,1:05:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感觉了吧\N同事会看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:15.38,1:06:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:19.54,1:06:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:32.02,1:06:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:42.74,1:06:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不行吧\N你很想要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:51.38,1:06:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我会发出声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:55.38,1:07:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不能忍耐呢\N抱歉 太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:02.26,1:07:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我道歉\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:06.58,1:07:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你的大声嚷嚷道歉\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:15.70,1:07:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你一直淫叫道歉\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:37.46,1:07:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看最深处\N在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:48.82,1:07:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开让我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:11.86,1:08:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还没被看过呢\N请看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:20.34,1:08:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会害羞啊\N会
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:32.02,1:08:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来这
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:39.22,1:08:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长\N快舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:07.54,1:09:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边舔我边帮自己用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:36.18,1:09:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真喜欢肉棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:50.58,1:10:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 我就只能做到这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:57.14,1:10:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:01.46,1:11:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那分手吧\N怎么这样 不要跟我分手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:10.10,1:11:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:26.42,1:11:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:47.70,1:11:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方 我会高潮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:11.70,1:12:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.66,1:12:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:35.70,1:12:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:41.46,1:12:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动这么快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:47.70,1:12:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被听到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:54.42,1:12:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:31.70,1:13:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 会发出声音的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:39.70,1:13:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴会高潮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:44.66,1:13:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:18.58,1:14:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:50.58,1:15:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了 要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:45.46,1:16:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 小穴好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:32.18,1:17:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴好开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:52.18,1:17:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:00.34,1:18:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:07.38,1:18:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:16.50,1:18:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 人家小穴好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:46.42,1:18:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:23.54,1:19:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然没我不行\N没有部长的蛋蛋就活不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:31.38,1:19:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说这种话 我们不能在这 分手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:41.78,1:19:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要跟我分手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:50.74,1:19:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我说什么你都会做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:56.66,1:20:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了部长的蛋蛋 我什么都愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:02.26,1:20:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我再想一想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:08.98,1:20:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您了 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:17.46,1:20:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 我又被那女的骂了\N又被骂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:25.46,1:20:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我只是太晚给他资料就被大骂一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:33.62,1:20:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的做不下去了\N对啊 她真的太严了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:41.78,1:20:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那种态度我很疲累
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:48.82,1:20:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长也不说说她\N真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:01.46,1:21:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了\N辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:04.18,1:21:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们工作辛苦了 谢谢\N所以我有帮你们准备一点东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:12.98,1:21:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:32.82,1:21:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长\N什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:37.94,1:21:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近你很常出错喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:45.62,1:21:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:49.30,1:21:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给部长添麻烦了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:55.86,1:22:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我说要跟你分手吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:04.18,1:22:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以最近才那么常出错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:09.46,1:22:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 我想待在部长身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:15.86,1:22:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:19.06,1:22:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我待在你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:24.98,1:22:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想待在我身边 是\N不想离开我 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:32.34,1:22:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 不想分手啊\N我绝对不要分手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:39.06,1:22:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我想知道你有多喜欢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:45.62,1:22:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了\N部长说的话我都照办
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:57.14,1:23:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里给我看小穴\N在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:06.58,1:23:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里\N怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:11.38,1:23:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点脱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:14.26,1:23:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:18.74,1:23:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像用我的名义作威作福 我很不爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:33.14,1:23:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:37.78,1:23:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么退缩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:43.54,1:23:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:46.58,1:23:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 这里真的不行\N不要吵 快给我看小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:55.54,1:23:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:58.90,1:24:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:44.82,1:24:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 我把内裤脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:51.22,1:24:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:52.02,1:24:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看小穴啊 怎么了 不是说都会照办吗 \N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:59.22,1:25:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点给我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:08.34,1:25:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样吗\N这样看不到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:16.02,1:25:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 像这样吗\N这样完全看不到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:25.30,1:25:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经尽力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:33.94,1:25:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 把裙子脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:38.10,1:25:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:39.38,1:25:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被看到的\N没有人会注意的 大家都在认真上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:47.06,1:25:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裙子的话也太
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:52.66,1:25:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦 这样我们就分手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:59.06,1:26:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有这件事不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:04.18,1:26:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就快点脱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:08.98,1:26:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱我对吧\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:13.30,1:26:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢部长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:43.06,1:26:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错喔 很适合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:50.10,1:26:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手拿开\N让我看清楚你那
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:58.10,1:27:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 那我不能满足啊\N部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:13.78,1:27:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:18.26,1:27:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的淫荡小穴我看得很清楚啰\N请不要说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:29.46,1:27:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在让我看看你后面\N后面有人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:34.26,1:27:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很认真在开会 没人会转过来的 没时间了 快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:44.18,1:27:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 快点转过去 快点快点\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:06.26,1:28:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:18.26,1:28:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看的到你的小穴和屁眼喔\N请不要说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:28.34,1:28:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是没变 是个色女呢\N不要这样说我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:38.42,1:28:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:44.18,1:28:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说你是大色女吧\N这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:49.30,1:28:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说嘛 不说啊\N我说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:57.78,1:29:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你回家吧\N不要 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:05.62,1:29:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要走\N你乖乖嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:13.30,1:29:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不可以沉稳点 不然会被发现的 大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:24.34,1:29:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要给我看你的小穴就好了\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:32.66,1:29:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 不要走\N这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:38.90,1:29:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:50.58,1:29:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样很有感觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:04.82,1:30:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:13.30,1:30:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我装没事的样子 站好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:26.10,1:30:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:51.22,1:30:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎样\N对不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:57.94,1:31:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫那么大声是怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:02.90,1:31:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要大家来看是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:07.86,1:31:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种力道你就爽啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:17.78,1:31:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再吵分手算了\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:23.70,1:31:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长我真的会高潮的 不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:33.78,1:31:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 真的好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:46.74,1:31:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:50.74,1:31:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长\N乖乖转过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:57.78,1:32:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用普通的表情就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:01.62,1:32:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:08.34,1:32:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被听到的\N那就不要叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:13.62,1:32:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖听话\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:19.06,1:32:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:29.46,1:32:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦 会高潮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:04.82,1:33:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦 部长 我好像要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:09.94,1:33:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:15.38,1:33:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:21.14,1:33:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:35.06,1:33:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 你这样不行啦\N部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:40.50,1:33:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太快就高潮了\N你自己抓好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:48.66,1:33:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己做做看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:57.94,1:34:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准和我以外的人高潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:19.38,1:34:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:44.18,1:34:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:55.54,1:34:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会高潮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:01.46,1:35:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:04.82,1:35:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:21.78,1:35:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干嘛啊\N讨厌 不要看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:32.18,1:35:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以当社会人士吗 不要看\N帮我再看看资料吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:42.90,1:35:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 请不要看\N亏我们还这么努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:55.86,1:35:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:03.38,1:36:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:09.78,1:36:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样有办法好好上班吗\N不要再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:20.50,1:36:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:26.58,1:36:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放这要做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:35.54,1:36:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:43.06,1:36:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们开会原来都在做这种事\N没有 我们没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:51.54,1:36:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手拿来\N会被看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:08.18,1:37:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:18.90,1:37:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:25.62,1:37:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看\N真是淫荡的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:32.50,1:37:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N原来你一直在做这种事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:40.98,1:37:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 饶了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:52.98,1:38:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 不要\N舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:12.18,1:38:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:26.42,1:38:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:37.46,1:38:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:48.66,1:38:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:55.54,1:38:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:01.78,1:39:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:15.70,1:39:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 高潮了 小穴要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:28.98,1:39:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:36.34,1:39:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:43.06,1:39:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:58.42,1:40:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:15.70,1:40:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:20.18,1:40:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:29.94,1:40:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道她身材这么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:44.18,1:40:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很烦恼\N我有我的立场
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:52.02,1:40:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去我们都会被炒鱿鱼\N怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:58.26,1:41:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:03.22,1:41:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有好好按耐大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:08.82,1:41:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用嘴巴安慰大家\N对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:17.46,1:41:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:02.26,1:42:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也要 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:05.78,1:42:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我们两个忍耐吧 你也说你什么都愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:19.38,1:42:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 不听话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:24.66,1:42:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:28.66,1:42:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就好好取悦大家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:41.94,1:42:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:48.66,1:42:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家温柔点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:56.02,1:42:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:12.18,1:43:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样 不听话了\N没有这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:21.62,1:43:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说怎样都愿意吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:27.86,1:43:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:34.26,1:43:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不脱的话我们就结束关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:38.26,1:43:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有这个不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:42.26,1:43:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:56.18,1:44:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快脱 很快就结束了 不是说除了我都没感觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:03.70,1:44:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有感觉 那不就没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:42.90,1:44:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:54.58,1:44:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:17.14,1:45:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就完了\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:24.34,1:45:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:30.58,1:45:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我以外的人有感觉吗\N没
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:37.14,1:45:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 好啦我懂我懂\N就忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:54.58,1:45:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我以外的人有感觉吗\N没
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:00.34,1:46:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿喔\N好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:11.86,1:46:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:18.10,1:46:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腿张开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:41.78,1:46:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:47.22,1:46:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闻啊\N这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:53.78,1:46:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:12.02,1:47:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:17.14,1:47:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家轮流
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:28.34,1:47:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以插三根
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:32.34,1:47:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害\N你有在看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:36.18,1:47:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插了几只进去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:44.50,1:47:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 有感觉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:04.18,1:48:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:06.74,1:48:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要乱高潮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:11.22,1:48:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色女
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:28.02,1:48:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家舔舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:59.54,1:49:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能对我以外的人有感觉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:04.34,1:49:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我有感觉了 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:34.58,1:49:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很有感觉耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:39.38,1:49:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N好像乳头都硬起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:56.98,1:49:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:02.10,1:50:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:18.74,1:50:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:25.30,1:50:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很有感觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:30.26,1:50:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准对部长以外有感觉啊\N部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:35.86,1:50:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿啊\N大家不要看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:49.62,1:50:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 不要\N插进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:56.18,1:51:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表现得很好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:02.42,1:51:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很爽喔\N对不起 部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:22.26,1:51:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:40.50,1:51:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫得那么爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:57.30,1:52:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长我也忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:03.22,1:52:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会满足大家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:10.26,1:52:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有大家我们才能在一起\N部长不分手啰 恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:19.06,1:52:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是好同事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:31.22,1:52:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:39.54,1:52:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:47.54,1:52:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:56.98,1:53:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很爽吧\N好好看我肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:04.82,1:53:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很喜欢对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:11.38,1:53:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽 好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:19.22,1:53:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很厉害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:27.06,1:53:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃别人 吃很爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:33.46,1:53:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:36.98,1:53:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢别人的肉棒是不是\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:42.26,1:53:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢肉棒吧\N对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:56.02,1:54:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃吧\N部长
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:10.58,1:54:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:20.02,1:54:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长耶\N换我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:28.66,1:54:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真过分啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:33.62,1:54:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长我想跟你做\N不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:37.78,1:54:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要用嘴答谢大家\N我怎样都没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:48.34,1:54:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好色喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:53.78,1:54:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃喔\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:00.82,1:55:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了部长以外的肉棒 对不起\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:08.18,1:55:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人好像都不会满足\N真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:16.98,1:55:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:28.82,1:55:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也要\N好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:36.66,1:55:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了好多肉棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:56.66,1:56:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要啦 抱歉\N讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:05.62,1:56:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很忙\N真体贴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:11.06,1:56:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐吃我的肉棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:19.22,1:56:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它用干净喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:35.86,1:56:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:41.14,1:56:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽 好像做梦一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:53.30,1:56:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了 真的好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:09.30,1:57:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也舔我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:14.74,1:57:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爽啊 好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:31.86,1:57:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害\N是在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:40.66,1:57:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都可以插进去吗\N部长 可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:48.66,1:57:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都忍那么久了 就插吧\N不要 我只要部长的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:58.74,1:58:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你不是对别人的没感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:04.18,1:58:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:13.30,1:58:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里来舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:20.18,1:58:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:53.46,1:59:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 插我吧\N你要先让其他人爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:03.86,1:59:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:42.10,1:59:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会有感觉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:08.82,2:00:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:21.46,2:00:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:41.78,2:00:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很敏感喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:55.54,2:00:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高湖了 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:00.82,2:01:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们分手吧\N不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:07.38,2:01:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力不高潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:12.98,2:01:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 反正其他人也爽\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:45.46,2:01:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽喔 又要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:49.46,2:01:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了 要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:02.90,2:02:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能高潮啊\N还有很多根
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:08.02,2:02:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:22.90,2:02:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:31.22,2:02:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:34.90,2:02:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家的小穴爽吗\N爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:44.34,2:02:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长的肉棒最舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:56.34,2:02:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔我
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:10.74,2:03:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在我面前啊\N部长 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:19.54,2:03:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能高潮喔 还有很多个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:30.74,2:03:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长的最舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:40.50,2:03:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得好滑喔 讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:51.70,2:03:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:04.82,2:04:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我跟部长的肉棒交换吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:12.34,2:04:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长 可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:15.54,2:04:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好满足喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:20.82,2:04:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:30.42,2:04:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真爽\N部长呢 部长在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:43.06,2:04:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长去哪了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:49.62,2:04:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:04:55.22,2:04:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:00.34,2:05:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会高潮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:16.34,2:05:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让部长以外的肉棒干还高潮\N部长 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:28.98,2:05:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:32.18,2:05:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:41.30,2:05:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来舔我嘛\N舔我的脏肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:51.86,2:05:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 好脏啊\N有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:00.02,2:06:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我变干净吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:10.58,2:06:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家开心不就是最棒的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:06:25.62,2:06:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高莲小姐很漂亮的
